00:33:59.950 --> 00:34:00.580
Dia melarikan diri.

00:34:01.320 --> 00:34:02.210
Tingyan benar.

00:34:02.670 --> 00:34:03.450
Proyek kanal

00:34:03.800 --> 00:34:05.170
